{
  "id": "adv_event_2310_01_04",
  "title": "本気で\nぶつかれる\n相手",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――That night",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……芽衣はどうしているかしら……\n明日、帰って来たら……ちゃんと私の気持ちを――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haah… I wonder what Mei is doing…\nWhen she gets back tomorrow… I’ll properly convey my feelings to her――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.066666619,
      "endTime": 12.4085939566,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10535.2604229
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 12.6019270419
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、見ーーつけた！！　すずにゃーーーーん！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I found you!! Suzu-nya~~~an!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.1666666667,
      "endTime": 18.8395010631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 18.9614289442
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣！？　帰って来るのは明日だったはずでは！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei!? You weren’t supposed to be back until tomorrow!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9614289442,
      "endTime": 22.9932654539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 23.1399319648
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃんに早く会いたくて！　寮にいないから\n探したよ～。芽衣ね、すずにゃんとケンカしに来たよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wanted to see Suzu-nyan as soon as possible! You weren’t at the dorm‚\nso I looked for you~. I came here to fight with you‚ Suzu-nyan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.1399319648,
      "endTime": 33.0948983193,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 33.2882315953
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、なるほど……私とケンカを\n……はい？　ケンカ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haah‚ haah‚ I see… You want to fight with me…\n…What? A fight?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.2882315953,
      "endTime": 42.9882312137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 43.2015644709
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃん。芽衣はね、すーーっごく怒ってるんだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Listen‚ Suzu-nyan. Mei is suuuper angry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2015644709,
      "endTime": 49.061564413700005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 49.2615644137
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣はすずにゃんとユニットを組んで\n一杯楽しいことをしようと思ってたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was hoping to do all sorts of fun things\nwith you as a unit‚ Suzu-nyan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.2615644137,
      "endTime": 55.355373827499996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "なのに、すずにゃんてば打ち合わせのたびに\n機嫌が悪くなって、いきなり怒って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ you‚ Suzu-nyan‚ you get all grumpy at every meeting‚\nand suddenly get mad…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.5553737322,
      "endTime": 62.206666770000005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣の話も聞いてくれないし……あれじゃ\nどうしたらいいか分かんないよ！　すずにゃんのバカ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t listen to Mei… I don’t know what to do anymore!\nYou’re such a fool‚ Suzu-nyan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.2020420073,
      "endTime": 70.03181524259999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 62.3941841647
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 70.2384820619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "な……なななっ……言わせておけば好き放題に……！\nあなたに何が分かりますの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-w-what… How dare you say such things…!\nWhat do you know!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.2384820619,
      "endTime": 77.3821281113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 77.5621284483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "私が熟慮に熟慮を重ねたアイデアの数々を\nセンスだけであっさりと打ち負かしていく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My ideas… The countless ideas I painstakingly crafted…\nyou just brushed them aside with your sense alone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.5621284483,
      "endTime": 85.0935794828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 85.2935795782
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "どうして私が、こんな屈辱を味わわなければ\nいけないんですの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why do I have to suffer\nsuch humiliation!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.2935795782,
      "endTime": 90.0799983022,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 90.2533322015
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣だって、すずにゃんとユニットを組むなら\nどうしたらいいかなってずっと考えてたよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei has been thinking a lot too about what would be good\nfor our unit‚ Suzu-nyan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.2533322015,
      "endTime": 95.9533322969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 96.1466653822
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "どうせ考えるといっても三分くらいでしょう！？\n私は三日三晩考え続けましたわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You probably only thought about it for like‚ three minutes!?\nI spent three days and nights thinking about it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.1466653822,
      "endTime": 103.25577697739999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 103.4024444896
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "それは凄いけど……途中で眠くならない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s amazing‚ but… Don’t you get sleepy?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.4024444896,
      "endTime": 108.9164356548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 109.1231022357
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、夜更けになるとついうとうとしてしまって……\nって、そんなことはどうでもいいですわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s true that I tend to doze off late at night…\nB-but that doesn’t matter!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.1231022357,
      "endTime": 117.340811777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 117.5074757098
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣だって、猫ちゃんの集会に行って\nどうしたらいいか一杯聞いて回ったんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I even went to a cat gathering\nand asked around for advice!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.5074757098,
      "endTime": 122.9554349421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 123.1687681037
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "え、それはすご……くないですわよ！　危うく騙される\nところでしたわ。というか猫の集会ってなんですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wha… That’s not amazing! I almost fell for that.\nWhat’s a “cat gathering” anyway!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.1687681037,
      "endTime": 133.8077478248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 134.0077478248
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃんなりに考えてることがあるのは分かったけど\nそれをちゃんと言ってくれなきゃ分かんないよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I get that you have your own thoughts‚ Suzu-nyan‚\nbut you have to tell me so I can understand!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.0077478248,
      "endTime": 140.36761377640002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 140.5209400653
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "練習の時だって、意地張って無理やり続けて\n怪我しそうになったことがあったし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You even pushed yourself too hard during practice\nand almost got hurt!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.5209400653,
      "endTime": 146.6645896434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 146.8512686888
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_04-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "なっ……それなら、ライブのMCで予定にない話題を\nいきなり切り出すのはやめてくださいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… then you shouldn’t suddenly start talking about things\nthat aren’t planned during the live MC segment!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.8512686888,
